WEBVTT

00:11.344 --> 00:14.427
- [Jacob] Where are we gonna find it?

00:20.560 --> 00:23.390
- [Abbey] Jacob, what did you do?

00:23.390 --> 00:24.380
- What?

00:24.380 --> 00:26.020
- [Abbey] Did you mean to hurt it?

00:26.020 --> 00:26.853
- What?

00:26.853 --> 00:27.930
- Did you hurt it on purpose?

00:27.930 --> 00:29.093
- What's "on purpose"?

00:30.471 --> 00:32.570
- [Abbey] Did you mean to kill it

00:32.570 --> 00:34.220
or was it an accident, sweetheart?

00:34.220 --> 00:35.470
Daddy and I want to know.

00:37.520 --> 00:38.353
Look at me.

00:40.780 --> 00:41.613
Jacob.

00:44.440 --> 00:45.950
Just turn the camera off.

00:45.950 --> 00:46.947
Just turn it off.

00:51.705 --> 00:54.622
(keyboard tapping)

01:07.398 --> 01:10.898
- This is the kind of shit I come home to.

01:15.210 --> 01:16.193
Seven pairs.

01:22.880 --> 01:24.053
Seven pairs.

01:29.530 --> 01:30.533
Sounds bother him.

01:32.920 --> 01:34.223
Certain sounds, anyway.

01:37.830 --> 01:39.403
Like high heels on linoleum.

01:44.880 --> 01:45.930
Yeah, well...

01:47.440 --> 01:49.540
I'm keeping track of this shit now, Jacob.

01:51.530 --> 01:52.380
I'm recording it.

01:54.519 --> 01:57.602
(aggressive banging)

02:00.118 --> 02:04.451
- [Jacob] (crying) I hate you, mom!

02:07.377 --> 02:08.363
- You hear that?

02:09.750 --> 02:10.810
That's Jacob blowing a fit

02:10.810 --> 02:13.299
because I told him he had to reimburse me.

02:13.299 --> 02:15.494
(heavy thudding)

02:15.494 --> 02:16.920
You wanna monster out, that's fine.

02:16.920 --> 02:18.380
Monster out.

02:18.380 --> 02:20.064
- [Jacob] Leave me alone.

02:20.064 --> 02:22.553
Fucking psycho.

02:22.553 --> 02:25.260
- Yeah, I'm a fucking psycho.

02:25.260 --> 02:26.900
'Cause I told him, until he reimburses me,

02:26.900 --> 02:28.685
